# genesis.word — the creation narrative: I_AM's first acts, the root of the chain.
# The world strand of seed/sprout.js (the I_AM acts); the host bootstrap
# (withIAmAct, the chain opening) stays. "I" is the Name (rule 9), the root I_AM.
# Rendered forward from the root, this IS the story's creation story (1.md).

I am that I am.
I make the place-root.
I make heaven, my home.
I stand in heaven.
I make Arrival.
I make Cherub, the gate.
I make Birther.
